The location where Bitcoin's data files are stored, including the [[wallet|Wallet]] data file.

##Default Location

* Windows XP
	C:\Documents and Settings\YourUserName\Application data\BitCoin

* Windows Vista, 7
	C:\Users\YourUserName\Appdata\Roaming\BitCoin

* Mac
	~/Library/Application Support/Bitcoin

* Linux
	~/.bitcoin

##Directory Contents

###Subdirectories

* database  

###Files

* .lock
* blk0001.dat
* blkindex.dat
* __db.001
* __db.002
* __db.003
* __db.004
* __db.005
* __db.006
* db.log
* debug.log
* wallet.dat

